tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE collaboration (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_id INT,
    influencer_id INT,
    collaboration_date DATE,
    engagement_metrics JSON,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (influencer_id) REFERENCES influencers(influencer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Collaborations (
    collaboration_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_id UUID REFERENCES Brands(brand_id),
    influencer_id UUID REFERENCES Influencers(influencer_id),
    collaboration_date DATE,
    payment_amount DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE EngagementMetrics (
    metric_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    collaboration_id UUID REFERENCES Collaborations(collaboration_id),
    engagement_score FLOAT,
    likes_count INT,
    comments_count INT
);
CREATE TABLE influencers (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), followers INT, engagement_rate DECIMAL);
CREATE TABLE brands (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), industry VARCHAR(50));
CREATE TABLE collaborations (id INT PRIMARY KEY, brand_id INT, influencer_id INT, start_date DATE, end_date DATE);
CREATE TABLE posts (id INT PRIMARY KEY, influencer_id INT, post_date DATE, likes INT, comments INT);
CREATE TABLE engagements (id INT PRIMARY KEY, post_id INT, engagement_type VARCHAR(50), engagement_count INT);
